1827038 15HBPenalty for contravention where no separate penalty has been provided.- Whoever fails to comply with any provision of this Act, the rules or the regulations made or directions issued by the Board thereunder for which no separate penalty has been pro ided, shall be liable to a penalty which may extend to one crore rupees.".
