1976007 32 Repeal and saving.-
1855358 1The Securities and Exchange Board of India (Amendment) Ordinance, 2002 (Ord. 6 of 2002), is hereby repealed.
431064 2Notwithstanding the repeal of the Securities and Exchange Board of India (Amendment) Ordinance, 2002 (Ord. 6 of 2002), anything done or any action taken under the principal Act as amended by the said Ordinance, shall be deemed to have been done or ta en under the principal Act, as amended by this Act. ----
SUBHASH C. JAIN,
Secy. to the Govt. of India.
